citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:30am-12:00pm
on 10-MAR-21. No response was received within 30 minutes to a voicemail left on the listed phone number as well as
horn honks from the driveway.
End Section
